At will: detect magic, fireball
3/day each: hold monster, wall of fire</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>0</attack_bonus><br></li><br></html>','','<html><br><li><br><name><text><b>Multiattack</text></name><br><desc><text><i>The pit fiend makes four attacks: one with its bite, one with its claw, one with its mace, and one with its tail.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>0</attack_bonus><br></li><br><li><br><name><text><b>Bite</text></name><br><desc><text><i>Melee Weapon Attack: +14 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 22 (4d6 + 8) piercing damage. The target must succeed on a DC 21 Constitution saving throw or become poisoned. While poisoned in this way, the target can''t regain hit points, and it takes 21 (6d6) poison damage at the start of each of its turns. The poisoned target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>14</attack_bonus><br><damage_dice><text>4d6</text></damage_dice><br><damage_bonus>8</damage_bonus><br></li><br><li><br><name><text><b>Claw</text></name><br><desc><text><i>Melee Weapon Attack: +14 to hit, reach 10 ft. , one target. Hit: 17 (2d8 + 8) slashing damage.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>14</attack_bonus><br><damage_dice><text>2d8</text></damage_dice><br><damage_bonus>8</damage_bonus><br></li><br><li><br><name><text><b>Mace</text></name><br><desc><text><i>Melee Weapon Attack: +14 to hit, reach 10ft., one target. Hit: 15 (2d6 + 8) bludgeoning damage plus 21 (6d6) fire damage.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>14</attack_bonus><br><damage_dice><text>2d6</text></damage_dice><br><damage_bonus>8</damage_bonus><br></li><br><li><br><name><text><b>Tail</text></name><br><desc><text><i>Melee Weapon Attack: +14 to hit, reach 10ft., one target. Hit: 24 (3d1O + 8) bludgeoning damage.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>14</attack_bonus><br><damage_dice><text>3d10</text></damage_dice><br><damage_bonus>8</damage_bonus><br></li><br></html>','',NULL);
-- REPLACE INTO `STANDARD_MONSTERS` VALUES (224,'Planetar','Large','celestial','','lawful good','19','200','16d10','40 ft., fly 120 ft.','24','20','24','19','22','25','','','12','','11','12.0','','','','','','','','','','','','11','','','','','all, telepathy 120 ft.','truesight 120 ft., passive Perception 21','16','','radiant; bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical weapons','','charmed, exhaustion, frightened','<html><br><li><br><name><text><b>Angelic Weapons</text></name><br><desc><text><i>The planetar''s weapon attacks are magical. When the planetar hits with any weapon, the weapon deals an extra 5d8 radiant damage (included in the attack).</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>0</attack_bonus><br></li><br><li><br><name><text><b>Divine Awareness</text></name><br><desc><text><i>The planetar knows if it hears a lie.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>0</attack_bonus><br></li><br><li><br><name><text><b>Innate Spellcasting</text></name><br><desc><text><i>The planetar''s spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 20). The planetar can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:
