2d6 + 3) bludgeoning damage.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>5</attack_bonus><br><damage_dice><text>2d6</text></damage_dice><br><damage_bonus>3</damage_bonus><br></li><br><li><br><name><text><b>Tusks (Boar or Hybrid Form Only)</text></name><br><desc><text><i>Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 10 (2d6 + 3) slashing damage. If the target is a humanoid, it must succeed on a DC 12 Constitution saving throw or be cursed with wereboar lycanthropy.</text></desc><br><attack_bonus>5</attack_bonus><br><damage_dice><text>2d6</text></damage_dice><br><damage_bonus>3</damage_bonus><br></li><br></html>','',NULL);
