<p>You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this weapon. When you hit a creature of the giant type with it, the giant takes an extra 2d6 slashing damage, and it must succeed on a DC 15 Strength saving throw or fall prone.<br>
<p> The sword also functions as a <i>wand of enemy detection.</i> It regains all of it''s expended charges at dawn and isn''t at risk of crumbling it''s last charge if used.<br>
